notes: G Kirsten retired hurt at 22/0 (spasm in the lower back)
Waqar took his 300th ODI wicket when he trapped Mckenzie LBW
Shoaib pulled a muscle in the 19th over after bowling 3.3 overs. Abdul Razzaq completed the over. He returned to bowl the 25th over, but only completed 2 balls of it. Razzaq again completed the over.

stories.title: Pakistan end South African winning spree
stories.summary:
Sharjah, March 28: One blistering over and it all made the
difference

stories.title: Pakistan win in stunning turnaround
stories.summary:
Pakistan snatched an incredible 67 run win against South Africa
at Sharjah today to end a run of 14 consecutive losses against
the Proteas and go into the final on Friday holding the
psychological whiphand
